---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-left">
      <span class="label">Zero to One</span>
      <p class="footer-tagline">
        솔로프리너와 소상공인을 위한 AI 의사결정 파트너.<br />
        만드는 과정을 공개한다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <nav class="footer-nav">
      <div class="footer-nav-col">
        <span class="label">탐색</span>
        <a href="/projects">프로젝트</a>
        <a href="/log">빌드 로그</a>
        <a href="/about">팀</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-nav-col">
        <span class="label">연결</span>
        <a href="/#newsletter">뉴스레터</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/jamusvii/zerotoone-site" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <div class="container footer-bottom">
    <span class="label">© {year} Zero to One</span>
    <span class="label">Build in Public — 수익도 실패도 공개한다</span>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: 8rem;
    padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .footer-tagline {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .footer-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .footer-nav-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .footer-nav-col .label {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .footer-nav-col a {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .footer-nav-col a:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .footer-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
